column5: Heading out to an eastern trib in the morning. Any reports from today?
They look good from what i've seen..
Rouge is OK vision wise, but is VERY low.
duffins was still fairly high and muddy yesterday, i couldn't get any action no matter what i tried (story of my life   ).
How'd ya make out ... was up at 5 this am .. thinking of heading east .. but by the time I got through the hunny-dew list it was noon
